metadata.name: 1. null > maxkochanov
metadata.description:
The very first artwork of a series exploring values and the role of personality in the NFT world.

Like a genesis block in blockchain this work describes the main principles of the experiment and starts a chain:

• In each work, the artist writes down the name (or a shortened wallet address) of the person who bought the previous one from the collection. This forms the name chain that always continues.
• The price always starts at 0.1 eth.
• The way of writing is always different.
